profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. Proudly serving all of Southern Ontario, we are Ontario's largest insulation company and are Energy Star and Foam Masters™ certified. Get in touch for a Free In-Home Assessment—contact us today to learn more.

profile:
J-P started working with his father in construction when he was just a child, his earliest memory is spending a day doing concrete work and then going to the candy store as payment.  From the experience he developed working with his father and having spent over a decade in the military, he learned the value of doing quality work with precision and the importance of being punctual. 
With over 30 years of experience in both commercial and residential projects under his belt, and from working directly with architects and engineers, he has the skills and confidence to make your vision become a reality. And if you’re lucky, he might bring a loaf of his famous sourdough bread.

profile:
We are a company of ardent renovation specialists serving Kingston, Ontario and the surrounding areas. We are custom painters, plasterers, carpenters, hardwood floor and dry wall installers, connected to many other trades with years of experience and references for any home improvement project you may have. We offer Professional Residential Contractor Services, specializing in Historical Home Restorations, Lathe and Plastering, Interior Design and Color Consultations, Additions, Flooring, Walls, Trim, Moldings, Tile and Marble Installations, Cabinets and Cabinet Refinishing.

We will increase the value and enhance the aesthetic appeal of your home. Whether it’s a Basement, Bathroom, Kitchen Design or any other custom renovation you may want, making living spaces beautiful and picture perfect is what we love to do. We treat every project as if it were our own home, to incredibly high standards, a level of service often lacking in today’s market place. Our work carries a warranty and is only done using absolutely the finest quality materials. Our clients love this approach as our testimonials indicate and we are always being called back for additional projects in their homes.
